sentences: She worked with film production company like 66 Dimension in 2007.
She returned to Nigeria in 2013 after her education program in the US.
She received the best Film and Director of the year by sisterhood award.

She started her education at Loral Nursery and Primary School, Festac town, Lagos after which she proceeded to the Federal Government College, Odogbolu for a few years and  she concluded her Secondary education in S-tee Private Academy, Festac Town.
